    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of uncompromising caliber. This specimen has been curated to meet the most exacting standards, exhibiting a showroom-grade exterior and a pristine, smoke-free interior. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and preserved in an immaculate state, it offers an unrivaled driving experience.",
